                Deworming and Parasites Control Program
            </h3>
            <p>
                Deworming treats and protects pets from Intestinal parasites which are harmful particularly to puppies and kittens and can cause diarrhea, dehydration and weight loss. it is usually done during vaccine appointment.
            </p>
        </section>
